The Proto-Mayan velar nasal *{{IPA|[<U+014B>]}} is reflected as {{IPA|[x]}} in the eastern branches (Quichean-Mamean), {{IPA|[n]}} in Q'anjobalan, Ch'olan and Yucatecan, [h] in Huastecan, and only conserved as {{IPA|[<U+014B>]}} in Chuj and Jakaltek.<ref>England (1994), pp.30<U+2013>31.</ref> 

